strings: <voice_0x01001CB0><se_high>Media princess: I will join the blood of Argonia soon...
<voice_0x01001CB1><se_high>Media princess: I think that it is my duty as a princess.
<voice_0x01001CB2><se_high>Media princess: Despite what you think, I can't even imagine marriage.
<voice_0x01001CB3><se_high>Media princess: I don't know what it means to be human...
<voice_0x01001CB4><se_high>Media princess: And ... I don't know how it feels to be away from you <hero>
<voice_0x01001CB5><se_high>Media princess: But the thought of not being able to control it sounds familiar. i am strong
<voice_0x01001CB6><se_high>Media princess: Farewell, <hero>, loyal guards of the castle...
